


=Summary=

As proposed by the [[European Sharing Economy Coalition]]:

* Help establish more housing cooperatives. 

* Permit residents to use their homes for short-term renters. 

* Amend or remove restrictions to co-habitation. 

* Enable the creation of co-housing and eco-villages.​


(http://www.euro-freelancers.eu/european-sharing-economy-coalition/)

